{"tid":1472495,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「繁體字」先係最正統既簡體字","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:11:58.000Z","uid":260041,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb466849533d16c66a3d8767624edea93644d9e","tid":1472495,"uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"簡體字：老毛時代產物<br />\n簡化字：文字演變的必然定律<br />\n<br />\n無話簡化唔啱，「繁體字」都係小篆既簡化字。<br />\n<br />\n但係我非常睇唔過眼啲五毛成日串9「繁體字」，所以先想大家一齊討論下。<br />\n<br />\n「繁體字」係可以係古文(包括小篆)睇出原形，係99%似樣。<br />\n<br />\n但係「簡體字」係根據「繁體字」改，改到不倫不類，根本就唔算得上正統。<br />\n<br />\n重話咩宋朝就有「簡體字」，又話日本既漢字有啲係簡體字=古代就有「簡體字」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無語言學/中文大佬入黎解釋下"},{"pid":"a9ba406b805aa12164f1d2c07d922705d5d6f01f","tid":1472495,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LYwMnOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLYwMnOu.jpg&h=d756b4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMWo9tu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMWo9tu.jpg&h=73eb92de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8e0459f09277045e895c0cd9e3144fe93f59ce2","tid":1472495,"uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9ba406b805aa12164f1d2c07d922705d5d6f01f","tid":1472495,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LYwMnOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLYwMnOu.jpg&h=d756b4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMWo9tu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMWo9tu.jpg&h=73eb92de&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}